claim.claim-text:
A library device comprising:
a mounting unit is adapted to mounted on a plurality of cartridges, and to include a top board having ejection holes, each of the ejection holes ejecting air that moves each cartridge toward the cartridge;
an air supplying device is adapted to supply the air to air supply channels connected to the ejection holes, respectively;
a plurality of valve devices are adapted to permit or intercept ejecting the air from the respective ejection holes;
a controller is adapted to open and close each of the valve devices so as to move each cartridge to a desired position; and
a drive device is adapted to insert and detach each cartridge on the top board into/from the library device, by using a hand device.
